A complete **end-to-end DevOps pipeline** featuring a Python application containerized with Docker, deployed on Kubernetes, and automated with a Jenkins CI/CD pipeline.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
devops-project/
├── app.py              # Python Flask/app entry point
├── Dockerfile          # Container image definition
├── Jenkinsfile         # CI/CD pipeline stages
├── deployment.yaml     # Kubernetes Deployment manifest
└── service.yml         # Kubernetes Service manifest
```

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| **Python** | Application logic |
| **Docker** | Containerization |
